title: Tulip Oval Coffee Table - Marble White Marble/Large
body: This Style Oval Coffee Table by&nbsp;Eero Saarinen,&nbsp;makes a mid-century statement in quality marble!&nbsp;Supported by a sleek yet stable base of cast aluminum finished in fresh white, the Oval Coffee Table&rsquo;s surface says low-key luxury with top-of-the-line Italian marble.
